===Etymology===
From {{bor|en|fro|triangle}}, from {{der|en|la|triangulum}}, noun use of adjective {{m|la|triangulus||three-cornered, having three angles}}, from {{m|la|trēs||three}} + {{m|la|angulus||corner, angle}}.

